external.gw.api.datamodel.upgrade

Interface IDatamodelChange<D extends VersionAction>

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    BeforeUpgradeVersionCheckWrapper, CreateSpatialIndexVersionTrigger, DropTableAfterUpgradeTrigger, DropTableIfEmptyVersionTrigger
    Deprecated. 
    External entities are deprecated. Please use the new Java API instead.

    @Deprecated
public interface IDatamodelChange<D extends VersionAction>
    A class containing the work for applying a datamodel change. This is composed of two parts: 1. Database upgrade version trigger, 2. XML upgrade version trigger.
